{"tid":2338663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12.24 和你報佳音，已因為狗隻佈防已取消活動","createTime":"2020-12-24T07:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T12:43:25.000Z","uid":94771,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d81c7fe831f2199ae5f87441ef914ea5c079dbd9","tid":2338663,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L18VGVa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL18VGVa.jpg&h=075c3533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong>點都做小小風險申報</strong></span><br />\n[size=3]<span class=\"red\"><strong>注意，在香港作明顯表態的行動階有風險，請自我思考可以接受的代價，<br />\n令外狗隻已經StandBy，請大家BE WATER及睇實唔同區哨情況 </strong></span>[/size=5]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[size=3]<span class=\"orange\"><ins>平安夜快閃行動取消公佈：</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">因為搞手經驗唔夠，太早公佈地點令到狗隻提早佈防，無咗快閃既效果。為咗手足既安全，經深思熟慮後正式宣佈取消呢個活動，兄弟爬山各自努力。[/size=5]</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSource : <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/xmas_eve_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmas_eve_hk&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=e47e41ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/xmas_eve_hk</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>至於</strong>【12.24平安夜燭光悼念活動】就仲未取消<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>有已經有新聞表示狗將會對平安夜作出行動，所以請小心集合地點會有大量狗隻<br />\n</ins></strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o48RZJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo48RZJM.jpg&h=2dd26485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動詳情<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/SilentCandleNight\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSilentCandleNight&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=3161c529\" 